rows.label: qev041302_MSG0001
rows.name:
Wow, yeah, the gold nopopotamus card.
I'd love to get a look at one of those bad boys.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041302_MSG0002
rows.name:
I doubt you'll find one very easily, but good luck in
your search![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041302_MSG0003
rows.name: Ooo, did you want to trade Miralife Cards?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041302_MSG0004
rows.name:
Sorry, but I don't really have any rare ones,
so I doubt you'd be interested in any of mine.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041302_MSG0005
rows.name: Hey, have you heard about Miralife trading cards?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041302_MSG0006
rows.name:
I kept seeing the younger kids buying them,
so I figured I should get in on some of that action.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041302_MSG0007
rows.name:
Big mistake! Ha ha ha! Now it seems like half my
paycheck goes to buying those little buggers.
They're just so addictive![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041302_MSG0009
rows.name:
...You're looking for the gold nopopotamus?!
That thing is a legend! The super rare of super rares![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041302_MSG0010
rows.name: I still don't even have a silver, let alone any golds.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041302_MSG0011
rows.name:
About the only thing I could offer you for that bronze
blatta would be this bronze cinicula card.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041302_MSG0012
rows.name:
Okay, it's a trade! I doubt you'll come across a gold
nopopotamus anytime soon, but I'll keep my fingers
crossed for you.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041302_MSG0013
rows.name:
You sure? Well, I doubt you'll come across a gold
nopopotamus very easily, but best of luck with it.[ST:wait ]
